name: Totem Series : Totem of Fatherhood #001
description:
Totem series #001
Totem of Fatherhood

an embracement of feelings bout how i thought of my oldman, that recently i have noticed that become a good parents is a rocky road to go, and all of a sudden all that hate and  insults inside my head to him changing into aweness and regrets, that slowly appears as i become a father too.

so this is for my oldman, and for encouraging myself and all the fathers on the world to become a good one for their kids and family

love 


___________________________________
Totem series tells you bout life, love, human instinct and many more to share in a form of a totem.
